This is Yoda : The Yorick Deconvolution Algorithm
need to install the OptimPack library from eric thiebaut :
http://www-obs.univ-lyon1.fr/labo/perso/eric.thiebaut/optimpack.html
to run this software
a version of this library is distributed with Yoda
to install the local version go to trunk/OptimPack-1.3.2 directory
yorick -batch make.i
make clean all install
for exemples of Yoda use check the content of check_yoda.i
